836|"violence inside the carpet."|FALSE
836|"Robert, with the air of one doing the only possible thing, rushed to the"|FALSE
836|"window and opened it. Anthea screamed, Jane burst into tears, and"|FALSE
836|"Cyril turned the table wrong way up on top of the carpet heap. But the"|FALSE
