836|"The fact that the nursery carpet was ruined occasioned but little"|FALSE
836|"surprise, nor was any one really astonished that bed should prove the"|FALSE
836|"immediate end of the adventure. It has been said that all roads lead to"|FALSE
836|"Rome; this may be true, but at any rate, in early youth I am quite sure"|FALSE
836|"that many roads lead to BED, and stop there--or YOU do."|FALSE
836|"The rest of the fireworks were confiscated, and mother was not pleased"|FALSE
836|"when father let them off himself in the back garden, though he said,"|FALSE
