836|"Anthea screamed."|FALSE
836|"'Oh, Panther, I didn't mean to hurt, really,' cried Cyril, clattering"|FALSE
836|"the poker back into the fender."|FALSE
836|"'It's--all--right,' said Anthea breathlessly, clasping the hurt hand"|FALSE
